release_note: Enhanced end to end encryption. To enhance privacy and security we ve added the industry standard AES 256 Advanced Encryption Standard with 256 bit key to encrypt all your content before it leaves your device. This is in addition to the existing to using encryption via https as it goes over the network to our servers. Now all content is also stored encrypted. The only time it is used unencrypted is when it is processed without metadata via OpenAI s LLM models to generate summaries and new prompts. ... and tons of bug fixes and behind the scenes optimizations.
Minor bug fixes and improvements color design refinements
Plus plan subscriptions Chose between different therapy modalities Daily affirmations

Hello! Thank you for using Basal. We hope it s helping you reflect and process your experiences. This release has only a few minor updates: The settings page has been redesigned to give you more options: enable disable and customize the time of your daily reminder notifications more options to get in touch and connect an option to deactivate your account switched the login page so that Register is shown first by default instead of Login switched the font to Inter Thanks again for using Basal. The next release will be major and exciting so looking forward to sharing more soon.
